ARMISTEAD
v.
WARE, et al. 384P17-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 1, 2018 Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, for Ware, Timoth, et al. James Gregory Armistead, for Armistead, James Gregory.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 14th of November 2017 by Petitioner for Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 1st of March 2018."
